org.dei.facts.parser

Class StateNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dei.facts.parser.StateNode

  • public class StateNode
extends java.lang.Object
    The StateNode class represents a state in the diagnostic state graph. It contains the state name, transitions to other states, and diagnostic information.
